# Internationalization (i18n) Rules

- Use next-i18next for translations and locale management
- Store translation files in `/public/locales/{locale}/{namespace}.json`
- Implement automatic locale detection and redirection
- Use proper number, date, and currency formatting for each locale (use Intl API)
- Support right-to-left (RTL) languages; test all layouts in RTL mode
- Use descriptive translation keys (e.g., 'login.button.submit', not 'btn1' or raw text)
- Organize translation files by namespace and language
- Test all supported languages for layout, content, and pluralization using i18n test utilities
- Use pluralization and interpolation features of i18n library in all dynamic text 